---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="CSAE Policy — Far Fox" description="Far Fox's standards and policies against child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE).">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 backdrop-blur-md bg-fox-bg/80 border-b border-fox-pink/10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src="/fox-logo.png" alt="Far Fox" class="w-8 h-8" />
        <span class="text-xl font-900 tracking-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Far Fox
        </span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://app.lovefarfox.com"
        class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple text-white font-700 text-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-fox-pink/25 transition-all duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Open App
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-28 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-900 tracking-tight mb-8">
        CSAE <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fox-pink to-fox-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-fox-text-light text-sm mb-8">Last updated: May 3, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-fox-text-light leading-relaxed">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">Our Commitment</h2>
          <p>
            Far Fox has a zero-tolerance policy toward child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE) in any form.
            Far Fox is a private, invite-only couples app. All users must be 18 years of age or older to create an account.
            The app is designed exclusively for adult romantic partners and does not permit minors to register or use the service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">Prohibited Content and Conduct</h2>
          <p>The following are strictly prohibited on Far Fox:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>Any sexual content involving minors</li>
            <li>Grooming, exploitation, or solicitation of minors</li>
            <li>Sharing, uploading, or distributing child sexual abuse material (CSAM) in any form</li>
            <li>Any conduct that facilitates or promotes the sexual abuse or exploitation of children</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Violations of this policy will result in immediate account termination and will be reported to the
            National Center for Missing &amp; Exploited Children (NCMEC) and relevant law enforcement authorities.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">Age Verification</h2>
          <p>
            Far Fox requires all users to be 18 or older. Account creation requires a valid email address and
            explicit agreement to our Terms of Service, which prohibit use by minors. We reserve the right to
            terminate any account we have reason to believe belongs to a minor.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">Reporting</h2>
          <p>
            If you encounter any content or behavior on Far Fox that you believe involves the sexual abuse or
            exploitation of a child, please report it immediately to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-fox-text">Far Fox:</strong>
              <a href="mailto:support@lovefarfox.com" class="text-fox-pink hover:underline">support@lovefarfox.com</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-fox-text">NCMEC CyberTipline:</strong>
              <a href="https://www.missingkids.org/gethelpnow/cybertipline" class="text-fox-pink hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">missingkids.org/cybertipline</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            All reports received by Far Fox will be reviewed promptly. Where required by law, we will report
            confirmed CSAM to NCMEC and cooperate fully with law enforcement investigations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">Enforcement</h2>
          <p>
            Far Fox reserves the right to remove any content, suspend or terminate any account, and take any
            other action necessary to enforce this policy. We cooperate fully with law enforcement agencies
            investigating violations of laws related to child safety.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-800 text-fox-text mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about this policy can be directed to
            <a href="mailto:support@lovefarfox.com" class="text-fox-pink hover:underline">support@lovefarfox.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
